[SPEAKER_01] a to već dosta dugo traje,

975
01:05:38,639 --> 01:05:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] sam analizirao

976
01:05:40,079 --> 01:05:41,659
[SPEAKER_01] hrvatsku povijest.

977
01:05:41,659 --> 01:05:43,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ništa drugo,

978
01:05:43,659 --> 01:05:44,659
[SPEAKER_01] izdok svoj obitelj

979
01:05:44,659 --> 01:05:45,340
[SPEAKER_01] i svog oca

980
01:05:45,340 --> 01:05:46,260
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje,

981
01:05:46,260 --> 01:05:47,760
[SPEAKER_01] koji je stradao

982
01:05:47,760 --> 01:05:49,019
[SPEAKER_01] od te komunističke ruke.

983
01:05:49,019 --> 01:05:51,659
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvati su

984
01:05:51,659 --> 01:05:55,059
[SPEAKER_01] stoljećima

985
01:05:55,059 --> 01:05:57,219
[SPEAKER_01] bili sluge.

986
01:05:58,440 --> 01:05:59,719
[SPEAKER_01] jer se pitate

987
