[SPEAKER_01] zašto hrvati

988
01:06:01,039 --> 01:06:02,199
[SPEAKER_01] tisuću godina

989
01:06:02,199 --> 01:06:02,780
[SPEAKER_01] nisu imali

990
01:06:02,780 --> 01:06:03,539
[SPEAKER_01] svoju državu.

991
01:06:03,539 --> 01:06:07,219
[SPEAKER_01] Tisuću godina

